paragraphs.title: 2 - Create table claim_saving
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS cloudfin.claim_saving;

CREATE TABLE cloudfin.claim_saving(
  claim_date DATE,
  last_name STRING,
  client_id INT,
  claim_number INT,
  claim_code DECIMAL,
  claim_amount DECIMAL,
  risk_factor DECIMAL,
  claim_adjustment DECIMAL
  )
STORED AS orc;
